display_name: Apnea-Hypopnea Index (NREM): (All apneas with no oxygen desaturation threshold used and with or without arousal + hypopneas with > 50% flow reduction and without oxygen desaturation threshold used and with or without arousal + hypopneas with > 30% flow reduction and with >= 3% oxygen desaturation or with arousal) / hour of NREM sleep from type I polysomnography
